data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER, BRING US AN OFFER! Adorable move-in ready home located in the desirable North Paulding schools, this home features 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, a bright and air kitchen overlooking a large private backyard, wood flooring on the main level plus new roof and windows. The lower level includes a 2-car garage, laundry area, and room for workshop/flex space. Ideal location right off hwy 61 within minutes of Burnt Hickory Park & schools.  This home qualifies for USDA 100% financing with zero down payment.
